# Topic Page Contract

Every topic page MUST render two sections/tabs:
A) THEORY (detailed)
B) PRACTICE (interactive)

THEORY must include:
- What you will learn
- Prerequisites
- Mental model
- Core concepts
- Design process (step-by-step)
- Trade-offs table
- Common mistakes
- Mini case study
- Interview Q&A
- References (stored in CMS; rendered on-page)

PRACTICE must include:
- Interactive demo + controls
- Visualization (observable difference)
- Timeline/event log
- Guided steps mode
- Hands-on task + solution reveal
